ed. I am also determining if the workspace is in the correct state. Secondary actions like marketplace integration are also being considered.\n\n\n**Clarifying Component Visibility**\n\nI'm now clarifying the NextBestAction component's visibility logic. The current rule is that the component *should not appear if there is no relevant user state.* This means, for instance, on first visit to `/build/assessment`, before any data entry or report compilation, the component is hidden. It only appears when a relevant state is present. I'm also confirming that this logic extends to the global `/build` page.\n\n\n"}}
