{"ts":"2026-06-26T23:02:32.590Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_start","contentType":"reasoning","reasoning":"**Defining the Animations**\n\nI'm now detailing the planned animations and interactions for the \"Sovereign Guide.\" I'm planning a subtle Framer Motion entrance using fade-in and slide-up. I'll also add a mouse-hover interactive spotlight. It will be a beautiful, cursor-following radial gradient glow, just like the PremiumCTA. Micro-interactions on hover are also planned, with scale and glow effects.\n\n**Implementing the Mobile Strategy**\n\nI'm now working on the mobile-first design. I'm focusing on responsiveness, planning for graceful layout collapsing. I want to transition from a side-by-side flow or centered grid to stacked blocks for all viewports. This will ensure text readability and accessible touch targets on all devices.\n\n**Listing the Implementation Steps**\n\nI'm now outlining the implementation steps. I will create `components/build/NextBestAction.tsx`, and register it in `components/build/index.ts`. I will also integrate the component into several key pages, including `app/build/assessment/page.tsx` (in the result panel), `components/sections/BlueprintGenerator.tsx` (in the result panel and the final step), `app/build/roi/page.tsx`, `app/build/proposal/page.tsx`, `app/build/talk/page.tsx`, `app/build/sandbox/page.tsx`, and `app/build/marketplace/page.tsx` (all in their completed states).\n\n\n","redacted":false}}
