{"ts":"2026-06-26T23:03:14.897Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_end","contentType":"reasoning","reasoning":"**Designing NextBestAction Component**\n\nI'm thinking this PremiumCTA is really inspiring. I want to build a `NextBestAction` component based on its pattern, and expand on it. So, I'm aiming to perfectly capture the style and theme. I'll need to create the component file now: `components/build/Next`.\n\n\n**Defining the Configuration**\n\nI've got the `NextBestAction` component's initial structure laid out, including imports and utilities. I'm focusing now on the configuration mapping for the different build tools. I've drafted a `NextBestActionConfig` interface to manage the details of each recommendation. I've started defining its properties, ensuring that I have all the necessary information, such as tool names, titles, explanations, and visual styling cues. I am double checking the specific recommendations based on each stage that have been requested in the design.\n\n\n**Mapping the Route Logic**\n\nI'm now detailing the configuration maps. I've translated the requested recommendations into a structured format for the `NextBestActionConfig`. I've started mapping each step to the correct route, including the current tool, the recommended tool, route, secondary action, and secondary route. For example, in the assessment stage, I have a blueprint generator route, and the ROI calculator route as a secondary action.\n\n\n**Expanding the Component's Scope**\n\nI've added configurations for `/build/sandbox`, defining a title and explanation for the \"Compile Your Enterprise Statement of Work\" feature. I've also integrated the `talk` configuration, mapping it to the Blueprint Generator route and incorporating secondary actions like the Readiness Assessor. Moreover, I'm now detailing the `sandbox` configuration, which covers the Foundry Studio recommendation and its associated routes, along with the Agent Marketplace.\n\n\n**Refining Conditional Logic**\n\nI'm now refining the conditions for displaying the component. I've realized I need a more robust approach to determine \"relevant state.\" I'm planning to check local storage for tool-specific data and incorporate a `completed` prop to handle scenarios where the UI and local storage are out of sync. I am considering the scenarios for the `assessment` tool, and how to deal with the results view and state updates. I also added configurations for the Agent Marketplace, mapping it to the Execution Sandbox route with \"Simulate Mapped Recipes in Sandbox\" as the title.\n\n\n**Implementing State Checks**\n\nI've implemented a robust `checkState` helper function to determine component visibility, using local storage and tool-specific data. This addresses potential state discrepancies between the UI and local storage. I'm focusing on the `assessment` tool, and finalized the conditional logic that checks for blueprint history. The `GFFWorkspace` interface and related utilities have been correctly imported from the workspace utility file to ensure data integrity.\n\n\n**Planning the Sovereign Guide**\n\nI'm now formulating a design plan for the \"NextBestAction\" panel, which I'm calling the \"Sovereign Guide.\" I've outlined the page narrative, envisioning it as an interactive guide that detects local progress through the GFF AI workflow tools. I've chosen a visual metaphor of an air-gapped transit line with glassmorphism, animated light trails, and SVG transitions. The layout will be a centrally balanced block with premium typography, dual CTAs, and a routing map visual.\n\n\n**Defining the Animations**\n\nI'm now detailing the planned animations and interactions for the \"Sovereign Guide.\" I'm planning a subtle Framer Motion entrance using fade-in and slide-up. I'll also add a mouse-hover interactive spotlight. It will be a beautiful, cursor-following radial gradient glow, just like the PremiumCTA. Micro-interactions on hover are also planned, with scale and glow effects.\n\n**Implementing the Mobile Strategy**\n\nI'm now working on the mobile-first design. I'm focusing on responsiveness, planning for graceful layout collapsing. I want to transition from a side-by-side flow or centered grid to stacked blocks for all viewports. This will ensure text readability and accessible touch targets on all devices.\n\n**Listing the Implementation Steps**\n\nI'm now outlining the implementation steps. I will create `components/build/NextBestAction.tsx`, and register it in `components/build/index.ts`. I will also integrate the component into several key pages, including `app/build/assessment/page.tsx` (in the result panel), `components/sections/BlueprintGenerator.tsx` (in the result panel and the final step), `app/build/roi/page.tsx`, `app/build/proposal/page.tsx`, `app/build/talk/page.tsx`, `app/build/sandbox/page.tsx`, and `app/build/marketplace/page.tsx` (all in their completed states).\n\n\n**Reviewing Code Dependencies**\n\nI'm now diving into the code. I'm focusing on writing `components/build/NextBestAction.tsx`. Before coding, I'm checking the imported dependencies to ensure everything is correct. I am looking at how `motion` and `AnimatePresence` are imported, and how they're declared and used, and finding that using `import { motion, AnimatePresence } from \"motion/react\"` is the correct approach since it is already employed successfully elsewhere.\n\n\n**Coding the New Component**\n\nI'm now fully immersed in coding the `NextBestAction` component. I've designed the layout, incorporating rounded boxes with neon highlights matching the GFF color palette. I've begun to render a \"ACTIVE INSIGHT\" indicator, recommendation title, and explanatory text. I'm focusing on the interactive routing map and primary/secondary CTAs, which will be styled using the GFF color tokens.\n\n\n"}}
{"ts":"2026-06-26T23:03:14.900Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_start","contentType":"tool","toolName":"editor","toolCallId":"ncuee40d","input":{"path":"/Users/ayushbansal/Documents/GitHub/hirezapp_landing_page/components/build/NextBestAction.tsx","old_text":null,"new_text":"\"use client\";\n\nimport React, { useState, useRef, useEffect, MouseEvent } from \"react\";\nimport Link from \"next/link\";\nimport { motion, AnimatePresence } from \"motion/react\";\nimport { getFullWorkspace, getBlueprintHistory, GFFWorkspace } from \"./workspaceUtility\";\n\ninterface NextBestActionProps {\n  currentTool: keyof GFFWorkspace | \"blueprint\";\n  completed?: boolean;\n}\n\ninterface ActionConfig {\n  nextToolId: string;\n  nextToolName: string;\n  nextToolSub: string;\n  nextToolHref: string;\n  title: string;\n  explanation: string;\n  secondaryLabel: string;\n  secondaryHref: string;\n  accentColor: string;\n  glowColor: string;\n}\n\nconst CONFIGS: Record<string, ActionConfig> = {\n  assessment: {\n    nextToolId: \"blueprint\",\n    nextToolName: \"Blueprint Generator\",\n    nextToolSub: \"Sovereign Topology\",\n    nextToolHref: \"/build/blueprint\",\n    title: \"Generate Sovereign Architectural Blueprint\",\n    explanation: \"Based on your compiled 8-dimensional readiness scores, construct a system-level deployment graph mapping your private cloud isolation boundaries, routing latencies, and security supervisors.\",\n    secondaryLabel: \"ROI Savings Modeler\",\n    secondaryHref: \"/build/roi\",\n    accentColor: \"#9D00FF\",\n    glowColor: \"rgba(157, 0, 255, 0.15)\",\n  },\n  blueprint: {\n    nextToolId: \"roi\",\n    nextToolName: \"ROI Calculator\",\n    nextToolSub: \"Savings Model\",\n    nextToolHref: \"/build/roi\",\n    title: \"Model Sovereign Economic Impact (ROI)\",\n    explanation: \"Translate your completed architectural topology diagram into a precise multi-year cost saving and efficiency multiplier baseline customized to your industry.\",\n    secondaryLabel: \"SOW Proposal Studio\",\n    secondaryHref: \"/build/proposal\",\n    accentColor: \"#E4000F\",\n    glowColor: \"rgba(228, 0, 15, 0.15)\",\n  },\n  roi: {\n    nextToolId: \"proposal\",\n    nextToolName: \"Proposal Studio\",\n    nextToolSub: \"Statement of Work\",\n    nextToolHref: \"/build/proposal\",\n    title: \"Compile Enterprise Statement of Work\",\n    explanation: \"Convert your modeled economic variables and cost efficiency baseline into an executive-ready Statement of Work detailing licensing structures and implementation timelines.\",\n    secondaryLabel: \"Execution Sandbox\",\n    secondaryHref: \"/build/sandbox\",\n    accentColor: \"#3B82F6\",\n    glowColor: \"rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.15)\",\n  },\n  talk: {\n    nextToolId: \"blueprint\",\n    nextToolName: \"Blueprint Generator\",\n    nextToolSub: \"Sovereign Topology\",\n    nextToolHref: \"/build/blueprint\",\n    title: \"Synthesize Conversational Intake into Blueprint\",\n    explanation: \"Transform your mapped legacy process variables and priority urgency indexes into a functional, secure visual agentic deployment graph.\",\n    secondaryLabel: \"Readiness Assessor\",\n    secondaryHref: \"/build/assessment\",\n    accentColor: \"#9D00FF\",\n    glowColor: \"rgba(157, 0, 255, 0.15)\",\n  },\n  sandbox: {\n    nextToolId: \"foundryStudio\",\n    nextToolName: \"Foundry Studio\",\n    nextToolSub: \"Custom workflow DAG\",\n    nextToolHref: \"/build/foundry-studio\",\n    title: \"Graduate into Custom Workflow DAGs\",\n    explanation: \"Convert your sandbox simulation experiments into bespoke agent configurations. Formulate custom task nodes, vector knowledge bases, and multi-stage pipelines.\",\n    secondaryLabel: \"Agent Marketplace\",\n    secondaryHref: \"/build/marketplace\",\n    accentColor: \"#00FF9D\",\n    glowColor: \"rgba(0, 255, 157, 0.15)\",\n  },\n  marketplace: {\n    nextToolId: \"sandbox\",\n    nextToolName: \"Execution Sandbox\",\n    nextToolSub: \"Simulation Spec\",\n    nextToolHref: \"/build/sandbox\",\n    title: \"Simulate Marketplace Recipes in Sandbox\",\n    explanation: \"Deploy your compared agent recipes directly into our zero-retention execution sandbox to evaluate transactional speeds and security guardrails under simulated load.\",\n    secondaryLabel: \"SOW Proposal Studio\",\n    secondaryHref: \"/build/proposal\",\n    accentColor: \"#009DFF\",\n    glowColor: \"rgba(0, 157, 255, 0.15)\",\n  },\n};\n\n// SVG Icon helpers\nconst getToolIcon = (id: string, color: string) => {\n  const css = \"w-5 h-5 transition-colors duration-300\";\n  switch (id) {\n    case \"assessment\":\n      return (\n        <svg className={css} fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke={color} strokeWidth={1.5}>\n          <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" d=\"M9 12.75 11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 0 1 3.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 0 0 3 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285Z\" />\n        </svg>\n      );\n    case \"blueprint\":\n      return (\n        <svg className={css} fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke={color} strokeWidth={1.5}>\n          <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" d=\"m21 7.5-9-5.25L3 7.5m18 0-9 5.25m9-5.25v9l-9 5.25M3 7.5l9 5.25M3 7.5v9l9 5.25m0-9v9\" />\n        </svg>\n      );\n    case \"roi\":\n      return (\n        <svg className={css} fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke={color} strokeWidth={1.5}>\n          <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" d=\"M2.25 18.75a60.07 60.07 0 0 1 15.797 2.101c.727.198 1.453-.342 1.453-1.096V18.75M3.75 4.5h.007m-.007 3h.007m-.007 3h.007m0 2.25H21a.75.75 0 0 1 .75.75v1.5a.75.75 0 0 1-.75.75H3.75a3 3 0 0 1-3-3V1.5a.75.75 0 0 1 .75-.75h1.5a.75.75 0 0 1 .75.75V4.5Z\" />\n        </svg>\n      );\n    case \"proposal\":\n      return (\n        <svg className={css} fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke={color} strokeWidth={1.5}>\n          <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" d=\"M19.5 14.25v-2.625a3.375 3.375 0 0 0-3.375-3.375h-1.5A1.125 1.125 0 0 1 13.5 7.125v-1.5a3.375 3.375 0 0 0-3.375-3.375H8.25m0 12.75h7.5m-7.5 3H12M10.5 2.25H5.625c-.621 0-1.125.504-1.125 1.125v17.25c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125h12.75c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V11.25a9 9 0 0 0-9-9Z\" />\n        </svg>\n      );\n    case \"talk\":\n      return (\n        <svg className={css} fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke={color} strokeWidth={1.5}>\n          <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" d=\"M8.625 9.75a.375.375 0 1 1-.75 0 .375.375 0 0 1 .75 0Zm0 0H8.25m4.125 0a.375.375 0 1 1-.75 0 .375.375 0 0 1 .75 0Zm0 0H12m4.125 0a.375.375 0 1 1-.75 0 .375.375 0 0 1 .75 0Zm0 0h-.375m-13.5 3.01h18c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V5.625c0-.621-.504-1.125-1.125-1.125h-18c-.621 0-1.125.504-1.125 1.125v6.375c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125Zm18.375 3.375a.375.375 0 1 1-.75 0 .375.375 0 0 1 .75 0Zm0 0H18m-11.25 3h.008v.008H6.75V19.5Zm0-3h.008v.008H6.75v-.008Zm0-3h.008v.008H6.75v-.008Zm3 3h.008v.008H9.75V19.5Zm0-3h.008v.008H9.75v-.008Zm0-3h.008v.008H9.75v-.008Zm3 3h.008v.008h-.008V19.5Zm0-3h.008v.008h-.008v-.008Zm0-3h.008v.008h-.008v-.008Z\" />\n        </svg>\n      );\n    case \"sandbox\":\n      return (\n        <svg className={css} fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke={color} strokeWidth={1.5}>\n          <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" d=\"M14.25 9.75 16.5 12l-2.25 2.25m-4.5 0L7.5 12l2.25-2.25M6 20.25h12A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 20.25 18V6A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 18 3.75H6A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 3.75 6v12A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 6 20.25Z\" />\n        </svg>\n      );\n    case \"marketplace\":\n      return (\n        <svg className={css} fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke={color} strokeWidth={1.5}>\n          <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" d=\"M13.5 21v-7.5a.75.75 0 0 1 .75-.75h3a.75.75 0 0 1 .75.75V21m-4.5 0H2.36m11.14 0H18m0 0h3.64m-1.39 0V9.349M3.75 21V9.349m0 0a3.001 3.001 0 0 0 3.75-.615A2.993 2.993 0 0 0 9.75 9.75c.896 0 1.7-.393 2.25-1.016a2.993 2.993 0 0 0 2.25 1.016c.896 0 1.7-.393 2.25-1.015a3.001 3.001 0 0 0 3.75.614m-16.5 0a3.004 3.004 0 0 1-.621-4.72l1.189-1.19A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 5.378 3h13.243a1.5 1.5 0 0 1 1.06.44l1.19 1.189a3 3 0 0 1-.621 4.72M6.75 18h3.5a.75.75 0 0 0 .75-.75V13.5a.75.75 0 0 0-.75-.75h-3.5a.75.75 0 0 0-.75.75v3.75c0 .414.336.75.75.75Z\" />\n        </svg>\n      );\n    case \"foundryStudio\":\n    default:\n      return (\n        <svg className={css} fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke={color} strokeWidth={1.5}>\n          <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" d=\"M18 18.72a9.094 9.094 0 0 0 3.741-.479 3 3 0 0 0-4.682-2.72m.94 3.198.001.031c0 .225-.012.447-.037.666A11.944 11.944 0 0 1 12 21c-2.17 0-4.207-.576-5.963-1.584A6.062 6.062 0 0 1 6 18.719m12 0a5.971 5.971 0 0 0-.941-3.197m0 0A5.995 5.995 0 0 0 12 12.75a5.995 5.995 0 0 0-5.058 2.772m0 0a3 3 0 0 0-4.681 2.72 8.986 8.986 0 0 0 3.74.477m.94-3.197a5.971 5.971 0 0 0-.94 3.197M15 6.75a3 3 0 1 1-6 0 3 3 0 0 1 6 0Zm6 3a2.25 2.25 0 1 1-4.5 0 2.25 2.25 0 0 1 4.5 0Zm-13.5 0a2.25 2.25 0 1 1-4.5 0 2.25 2.25 0 0 1 4.5 0Z\" />\n        </svg>\n      );\n  }\n};\n\nconst getToolName = (id: string) => {\n  switch (id) {\n    case \"assessment\": return \"Readiness Assessor\";\n    case \"blueprint\": return \"Blueprint Generator\";\n    case \"roi\": return \"ROI Calculator\";\n    case \"proposal\": return \"Proposal Studio\";\n    case \"talk\": return \"Talk to Agent\";\n    case \"sandbox\": return \"Execution Sandbox\";\n    case \"marketplace\": return \"Agent Marketplace\";\n    case \"foundryStudio\": return \"Foundry Studio\";\n    default: return id;\n  }\n};\n\nexport default function NextBestAction({ currentTool, completed = false }: NextBestActionProps) {\n  const [isVisible, setIsVisible] = useState(false);\n  const containerRef = useRef<HTMLDivElement>(null);\n  const [coords, setCoords] = useState({ x: 0, y: 0 });\n  const [isHovered, setIsHovered] = useState(false);\n\n  useEffect(() => {\n    // Determine visibility based on completed prop OR stored local state\n    if (completed) {\n      setIsVisible(true);\n      return;\n    }\n\n    const checkLocalState = () => {\n      try {\n        if (currentTool === \"blueprint\") {\n          return getBlueprintHistory().length > 0;\n        }\n        const ws = getFullWorkspace();\n        const state = ws[currentTool as keyof GFFWorkspace];\n        if (!state) return false;\n\n        // Specific validity checks to ensure real state was completed\n        if (currentTool === \"assessment\") {\n          return !!state.showResult;\n        }\n        if (currentTool === \"talk\") {\n          return !!state.showResults || !!state.data;\n        }\n        return true;\n      } catch {\n        return false;\n      }\n    };\n\n    setIsVisible(checkLocalState());\n\n    // Listen to localstorage updates in case they complete it in real-time\n    const handleStorage = () => {\n      setIsVisible(checkLocalState());\n    };\n    window.addEventListener(\"storage\", handleStorage);\n    // Custom event dispatch in case of same-window SPA navigation updates\n    window.addEventListener(\"gff_workspace_update\", handleStorage);\n\n    return () => {\n      window.removeEventListener(\"storage\", handleStorage);\n      window.removeEventListener(\"gff_workspace_update\", handleStorage);\n    };\n  }, [currentTool, completed]);\n\n  const handleMouseMove = (e: MouseEvent<HTMLDivElement>) => {\n    if (!containerRef.current) return;\n    const rect = containerRef.current.getBoundingClientRect();\n    setCoords({\n      x: e.clientX - rect.left,\n      y: e.clientY - rect.top,\n    });\n  };\n\n  const config = CONFIGS[currentTool];\n\n  if (!isVisible || !config) return null;\n\n  return (\n    <AnimatePresence>\n      <motion.div\n        initial={{ opacity: 0, y: 30 }}\n        animate={{ opacity: 1, y: 0 }}\n        exit={{ opacity: 0, y: 20 }}\n        transition={{ duration: 0.5, ease: \"easeOut\" }}\n        className=\"w-full mt-12\"\n      >\n        <div\n          ref={containerRef}\n          onMouseMove={handleMouseMove}\n          onMouseEnter={() => setIsHovered(true)}\n          onMouseLeave={() => setIsHovered(false)}\n          className=\"relative w-full overflow-hidden rounded-[24px] border border-white/5 bg-[#030305]/90 backdrop-blur-[12px] p-6 md:p-8 lg:p-10 shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 hover:border-white/10 group\"\n        >\n          {/* Spotlight laser glow */}\n          <div\n            className=\"absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none transition-all duration-300 opacity-80\"\n            style={{\n              background: isHovered\n                ? `radial-gradient(circle 380px at ${coords.x}px ${coords.y}px, ${config.glowColor}, rgba(0, 157, 255, 0.02), transparent 75%)`\n                : `radial-gradient(circle 380px at 50% 50%, ${config.glowColor} 20%, transparent 80%)`,\n            }}\n          />\n\n          {/* Micro-mechanical high tech details */}\n          <div className=\"absolute top-0 left-0 w-6 h-6 border-t border-l border-white/10 rounded-tl-[24px]\" />\n          <div className=\"absolute top-0 right-0 w-6 h-6 border-t border-r border-white/10 rounded-tr-[24px]\" />\n          <div className=\"absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-6 h-6 border-b border-l border-white/10 rounded-bl-[24px]\" />\n          <div className=\"absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-6 h-6 border-b border-r border-white/10 rounded-br-[24px]\" />\n\n          <div className=\"relative z-10 flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-8\">\n            <div className=\"space-y-4 max-w-3xl text-left\">\n              {/* Dynamic Ping Indicator */}\n              <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n                <span className=\"relative flex h-2 w-2\">\n                  <span className=\"animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full opacity-75\" style={{ backgroundColor: config.accentColor }} />\n                  <span className=\"relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2\" style={{ backgroundColor: config.accentColor }} />\n                </span>\n                <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-white/50\">\n                  Sovereign Workflow Guide // Recommendation Engine\n                </span>\n              </div>\n\n              <h3 className=\"text-xl sm:text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-extrabold text-white tracking-tight leading-tight\">\n                {config.title}\n              </h3>\n\n              <p className=\"text-xs sm:text-sm text-white/60 font-light leading-relaxed\">\n                {config.explanation}\n              </p>\n\n              {/* Related route secondary option link */}\n              <div className=\"pt-2 flex flex-wrap gap-x-6 gap-y-2 items-center text-[10px] font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-white/40\">\n                <span className=\"text-white/20\">Recommended Path:</span>\n                <span className=\"text-white flex items-center gap-1.5 font-bold\">\n                  {getToolName(currentTool)}\n                  <svg className=\"w-3 h-3 text-white/30\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\">\n                    <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" strokeWidth={2} d=\"M9 5l7 7-7 7\" />\n                  </svg>\n                  <span style={{ color: config.accentColor }}>{config.nextToolName}</span>\n                </span>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n            {/* Custom high-fidelity SVG connection visualizer */}\n            <div className=\"shrink-0 flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-black/40 min-w-[260px] md:min-w-[300px] h-32 relative overflow-hidden select-none\">\n              <div className=\"absolute inset-0 bg-grid-pattern opacity-10 pointer-events-none\" />\n              \n              <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between w-full px-6 relative z-10\">\n                {/* Current tool node */}\n                <div className=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-1\">\n                  <div className=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-[#020204] flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg group-hover:border-white/25 transition\">\n                    {getToolIcon(currentTool, \"rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4)\")}\n                  </div>\n                  <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-white/40 text-center w-14 truncate\">\n                    {getToolName(currentTool)}\n                  </span>\n                </div>\n\n                {/* Animated transition connector pipeline */}\n                <div className=\"flex-1 h-px bg-white/10 relative mx-3\">\n                  <div \n                    className=\"absolute top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-2 h-2 rounded-full shadow-[0_0_8px_currentColor] animate-pulse\"\n                    style={{ \n                      color: config.accentColor, \n                      backgroundColor: config.accentColor,\n                      animation: \"gff-slide-pipeline 2s infinite linear\"\n                    }}\n                  />\n                  <style>{`\n                    @keyframes gff-slide-pipeline {\n                      0% { left: 0%; opacity: 0; }\n                      15% { opacity: 1; }\n                      85% { opacity: 1; }\n                      100% { left: 100%; opacity: 0; }\n                    }\n                  `}</style>\n                </div>\n\n                {/* Recommended tool node */}\n                <div className=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-1\">\n                  <div \n                    className=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full border bg-[#020204] flex items-center justify-center shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(255,255,255,0.02)] transition\"\n                    style={{ borderColor: `${config.accent